data.description:
Introducing Your Dream Home in Burleson, Texas with Seller Financing Option Available at 6% interest with 20% down!
This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem has recently undergone a stunning transformation, making it the perfect place to call home. Freshly updated throughout, this residence shines with modern elegance. The heart of the home boasts a beautifully remodeled kitchen featuring new appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. Whether you're hosting family gatherings or cozy dinners, this space is sure to impress.
Location? You couldn't ask for better! Situated in a highly sought after Burleson Independent School District, your kids' education is in excellent hands. Plus, you're just a stone's throw away from a plethora of shopping centers, restaurants, hospitals, and entertainment options.
Commuting is also a breeze as this home is conveniently located just off the 35W, providing quick and easy access to the DFW metroplex. 

*property owned by REagent
